    <section id="faq" class="faq">
        <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">

            <div class="row gy-4">

                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="content px-xl-5">
                        <h3>Frequently Asked <strong>Questions</strong></h3>
                        <p>
                            Certainly! Here are some frequently asked questions (FAQs) related to our pathology labs, along with short notes:
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-8">

                    <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="faqlist" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">

                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h3 class="accordion-header">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-content-1">
                                    <span class="num">1.</span>
                                    Can I eat or drink before a pathology test?
                                </button>
                            </h3>
                            <div id="faq-content-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    For certain tests, fasting may be required. It's essential to follow any pre-test instructions provided by your healthcare provider or the lab.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><!-- # Faq item-->

                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h3 class="accordion-header">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-content-2">
                                    <span class="num">2.</span>
                                    Do I need an appointment for lab tests?
                                </button>
                            </h3>
                            <div id="faq-content-2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    Many pathology labs accept both walk-ins and appointments. However, it's advisable to check with the specific lab for their policy.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><!-- # Faq item-->

                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h3 class="accordion-header">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-content-3">
                                    <span class="num">3.</span>
                                    Can I request a copy of my test results?
                                </button>
                            </h3>
                            <div id="faq-content-3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    Yes, you can usually request a copy of your test results from your healthcare provider or the pathology lab. Privacy regulations may apply.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><!-- # Faq item-->

                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h3 class="accordion-header">
                                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-content-4">
                                    <span class="num">4.</span>
                                    How can I access my past test results?
                                </button>
                            </h3>
                            <div id="faq-content-4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    Your past test results are available through our secure patient portal. Log in using your credentials to view and download your complete medical history.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><!-- # Faq item-->

                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <h3 class="accordion-header">
